            "is_accepted": false,
            "last_activity_date": 1356782490,
            "creation_date": 1279716963,
            "body": "<p>In my opinion, private methods should not be tested. Tests are for interfaces (in the broad meaning of this word).<\/p>\n",
            "answer_id": 3299429,
